<Page x:Class="SWAN.Views.WikiPages.SA11_5_WikiPage"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      Title="WikiPage"
      HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
      VerticalAlignment="Stretch"
        Foreground="{DynamicResource TextFillColorPrimaryBrush}">

    <!-- Ensure FlowDocumentReader stretches to fill available space -->
    <FlowDocumentScrollViewer x:Name="flowDocumentScrollViewer" HorizontalContentAlignment="Stretch" ScrollViewer.CanContentScroll="True" PreviewMouseWheel="flowDocumentScrollViewer_PreviewMouseWheel">
        <FlowDocument x:Name="flowDocument" IsOptimalParagraphEnabled="True" IsHyphenationEnabled="True">
            <!-- Center-align the title to take up the entire frame width -->
            <Paragraph FontSize="30">

                <Run Text="SA-11(5): Developer Security Testing and Evaluation: Penetration Testing/Analysis" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>

            <!-- Left-align content -->
            <Paragraph TextAlignment="Left">
                <Run Text="Severity :" FontWeight="ExtraBold"/>
                <Run Text="High" FontWeight="ExtraBold" Foreground="Red"/>
            </Paragraph>
            <!-- Add more content as needed -->
            <Paragraph FontSize="30">
                <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                <Run Text="Control Extension" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>
            
            
            
            <Paragraph Margin="10,20,0,0" Tag="SA11_5_numberone">
                <Run Text="1." FontWeight="ExtraBold" FontSize="30"></Run>
                The developer shall perform penetration and fuzz testing to identify software/firmware vulnerabilities in executable code
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph TextAlignment="Left" Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <Run Text="Maps To:"  FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="15" ></Run>
                <Run Text="CCI-003190, 003191, 003192"  FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="15" ></Run>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                The organization requires the developer of the information system, system component, or information system service to perform penetration testing at an organization-defined breadth/depth and with organization-defined constraints.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                <Run Text="Implementation Guidance" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                The organization being inspected/assessed requires within contracts/agreements that the developer of the information system, system component, or information system service perform penetration testing at a breadth/depth defined in SA-11 (5), CCI 3191 and with constraints defined in SA-11 (5), CCI 3192.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                <Run Text="Validation Procedures" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                The organization conducting the inspection/assessment obtains and examines the contracts/agreements to ensure the organization being inspected/assessed requires that the developer of the information system, system component, or information system service perform penetration testing at a breadth/depth defined in SA-11 (5), CCI 3191 and with constraints defined in SA-11 (5), CCI 3192.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                <Run Text="Compelling Evidence" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                1.) System security plan (SSP).
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                2.) System development life cycle (SDLC) documentation.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                3.) Continuous monitoring plan must require developer to perform penetration testing at organization-defined breadth/depth and with organization-defined constraints defined in SA-11 (5), CCI 3191 and with constraints defined in SA-11 (5), CCI 3192.
            </Paragraph>



            <Paragraph Margin="10,20,0,0" Tag="SA11_5_numbertwo">
                <Run Text="2." FontWeight="ExtraBold" FontSize="30"></Run>
                The developer shall document the detailed results of penetration and fuzz testing activities in a SAER, and summarize in the SVAR.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph TextAlignment="Left" Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <Run Text="Maps To:"  FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="15" ></Run>
                <Run Text="CDRLâ€™s for SAER and SVAR"  FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="15" ></Run>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                MAPS TO DESCRIPTION
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                <Run Text="Implementation Guidance" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                Implementation guide description
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                <Run Text="Validation Procedures" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                Validation Proc Description
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="50,20,0,0">
                <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                <Run Text="Compelling Evidence" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="30" />
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph Margin="70,20,0,0">
                Evidence Description
            </Paragraph>
        </FlowDocument>
    </FlowDocumentScrollViewer>
</Page>
